{"tid":1486194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我在重申一次 連登沒有前線","createTime":"2019-08-18T19:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T10:03:33.000Z","uid":146917,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"44d35f9472e2c9813f90a54c8598ef37f71f1004","tid":1486194,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:58:01.000Z","msg":"應該係Baby Kingdom 同香討先有<br />\n班黑警咪撚再引用連登留言"},{"pid":"762c739a15012559d3727281dd19b21fbf2e94d4","tid":1486194,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:58:49.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦 連登毒撚連遊行都唔敢出 全部冷氣軍師黎"},{"pid":"1bbf691a1988f31549233549010b24538262a115","tid":1486194,"uid":62226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:00:26.000Z","msg":"TG先有前線"},{"pid":"2916dc5768a5fd0fd2bb91beec50eec1f9613737","tid":1486194,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:00:38.000Z","msg":"喺屋企發夢就有<br />\n前線都係香討班人嚟 一睇就知"},{"pid":"d1c3d08f4586e8fe0d212e81a808d05f52bc1cc5","tid":1486194,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"762c739a15012559d3727281dd19b21fbf2e94d4","tid":1486194,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:58:49.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦 連登毒撚連遊行都唔敢出 全部冷氣軍師黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:00:54.000Z","msg":"連登和理非集中營"},{"pid":"a7b734a248e125a41af5db8604b25beb9d7063cd","tid":1486194,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:02:19.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSss4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=12e82fc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSss4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=12e82fc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"78cb8daa395652ed6c95e672d7226e34429d31bc","tid":1486194,"uid":133525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:07:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔講就天下無敵，做就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成撚日開po屌人做得唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己就係屋企打飛機"},{"pid":"a4fa444acd5f0bb9f9cee1ae20d01db5b754301f","tid":1486194,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cd6ed17186569deee9639f09d245fd9f3f15a0","tid":1486194,"uid":146917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:09:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香討/baby condom 戰鬥完就貼現場開左幾多槍，<br />\n有幾多粒TG<br />\n<br />\n而連登 行完就貼自己隻腳有幾皺皮 <br />\n不停屌班前線要散水 可想而知<br />\n你話連登有前線邊撚個信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"df0829074eeb1f7fc34a3ae0cff8dd827c4a404d","tid":1486194,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:10:39.000Z","msg":"Rite, 阿蛇唔好再扮勇武啦，好辛苦呀你哋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add743ac5e582d9f94b397e776e1b473f34e8bad","tid":1486194,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06cd6ed17186569deee9639f09d245fd9f3f15a0","tid":1486194,"uid":146917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:09:04.000Z","msg":"<